<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA060494-0015 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 048103 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 4, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 8; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
