 Briseno joined his attorney, Gregory G. Petersen, for a news conference Friday 
outside the lawyer's office in Orange County. Briseno lost his countersuit 
against King this week, in which he alleged that King had struck him while he 
tried to handcuff King. The jury found that Briseno had been hit but refused to 
award punitive damages. 
</P>
