12-hour radiothon today to benefit the Leukemia Society of America (B17) . . . 
Humberto Hernandez, vice president and station manager for KMQA, La Maquina, 
says the Valley is an important target because it makes up about 50% of his 
station's audience. "If one quarter of our people in the Valley -- 25% of our 
audience -- makes pledges for this event, it would be a successful event," 
Hernandez said. 
