home tour today and Sunday between 10 a.m. and 4 p.m., featuring six homes 
built in the 1920s and 1930s and some of the neighborhood's best-kept gardens. 
</P>
<P>
 The ballet folklorico group, Relampago del Cielo, will perform traditional 
Mexican dances, and Bruce Gifford & the Jazz Generation also will perform. 
</P>
