</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 Trevor Brown, a second baseman at Troy High, has signed a letter of intent to 
play at Tusculum College, an NAIA school in Tennessee. Brown batted .310 this 
season with 20 RBIs and had a team-high eight doubles. 
</P>
