<P>
 33rd District race -- Charles E. Green, a candidate in the Democratic primary 
in the 33rd Congressional District, has run unsuccessfully for U.S. Senate 
three times and once for Los Angeles County sheriff. A story in the 
Southeast/Long Beach and City Times editions reported incorrectly that Greene 
had not run for office previously. 
